sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh Controller
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Inference Runtime<br/>(Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/models

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Load (Standalone Puller)
    MM->>Puller: gRPC LoadModel(modelId, modelKey)<br/>localhost:8084, plaintext
    Note over Puller: Parse storage credentials<br/>from modelKey JSON
    Puller->>Storage: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key / SA / SP
    Storage-->>Puller: Model files downloaded
    Puller->>FS: Write model to /models/{modelId}
    Note over Puller: Strip credentials from<br/>modelKey before forwarding
    Puller->>Adapter: gRPC LoadModel(modelId, localPath)<br/>localhost:8085, plaintext
    Note over Adapter: Adapt directory layout:<br/>Triton: config.pbtxt<br/>MLServer: model-settings.json<br/>OVMS: model_config_list.json<br/>TorchServe: .mar symlink
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model via runtime API<br/>Triton: gRPC RepositoryModelLoad (8001)<br/>MLServer: gRPC RepositoryModelLoad (8001)<br/>OVMS: HTTP POST /v1/config/reload (8001)<br/>TorchServe: gRPC RegisterModel (7071)
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Model loaded successfully
    Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModel response (sizeInBytes)
    Puller-->>MM: LoadModel response (sizeInBytes)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Load (Embedded Puller)
    MM->>Adapter: gRPC LoadModel(modelId, modelKey)<br/>localhost:8085, plaintext
    Adapter->>Storage: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: Provider credentials
    Storage-->>Adapter: Model files downloaded
    Adapter->>FS: Write model to /models/{modelId}
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model via runtime API
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Model loaded successfully
    Adapter-->>MM: LoadModel response (sizeInBytes)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Model Unload
    MM->>Puller: gRPC UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>localhost:8084, plaintext
    Puller->>Adapter: gRPC UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>localhost:8085, plaintext
    Adapter->>Runtime: Unload model via runtime API<br/>Triton: gRPC RepositoryModelUnload<br/>MLServer: gRPC RepositoryModelUnload<br/>OVMS: HTTP POST /v1/config/reload<br/>TorchServe: gRPC UnregisterModel
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Model unloaded
    Adapter-->>Puller: UnloadModel response
    Puller->>FS: Delete /models/{modelId}
    Puller-->>MM: UnloadModel response

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 4: Keras-to-TF Conversion (Triton only)
    Note over Adapter: Triton adapter detects .h5 file
    Adapter->>Adapter: subprocess exec<br/>/opt/scripts/tf_pb.py
    Note over Adapter: Python: Load Keras .h5<br/>Export TensorFlow SavedModel
    Adapter->>FS: Write SavedModel to /models/{modelId}
